Volkswagen to Invest 1 Billion Euros in Green Energy, FTD Says

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-08-25T19:02:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-25/volkswagen-to-invest-1-billion-euros-in-green-energy-ftd-says.html
Volkswagen AG (VOW)  plans to invest about
1 billion euros ($1.4 billion) in wind, hydro and sun energy in
the coming two years to cut its emissions of carbon dioxide and
may invest in  wind turbines  at sea,  Financial Times Deutschland 
reported in a preview of an article that will be published
tomorrow, without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  